OL,4,CShould disposable vapes be banned?
OL,5, Walk down the street, and you will
OL,6, probably spot finger-sized colourful
OL,7, plastic tubes discarded on the ground.
OL,9,FDisposable vapes are booming in
OL,10,Fpopularity, especially among those aged
OL,11,F18-34. They are easy to use and cheap.
OL,13,FBut campaigners say they are an
OL,14,Fenvironmental nightmare, One activist
OL,15,Fis calling for them to be banned.
OL,17,FThe vape industry told BBC News that
OL,18,Fthe problem lies with unclear disposal
OL,19,Frules and that there needs to be better
OL,20,Fnational schemes for recycling.
